# DESIGN SPECIFICATION

## Component Intelligence Applied
- **Typography Hierarchy**: Headline/Large for the main title, Title/Medium for section headers, Body/Medium for descriptions, Label/Medium for specifications labels, and Caption/Small for the last updated timestamp.
- **Spacing System**: itemSpacing of 16px for major sections and 12px for within sections, paddingTop of 16px on the root layoutContainer.
- **Component Behavior**: AppBar for top navigation with a back arrow, Bottom navigation for bottom tabs with semantic icon swaps, and Button component for primary and secondary actions with size and style variants applied.
- **Color Application**: White/white100 background, Primary/primary50 for primary CTA, Neutral/neutral90 for section headers and text, and Caption/Small for timestamp.
- **Layout Strategy**: Vertical layout for the main screen, horizontal for actions and image carousel.


## Domain Context Integration
- **Industry Patterns**: Follows standard e-commerce listing details page structure.
- **User Mental Models**: Core product information is prioritised at the top.
- **Contextual Adaptations**: Placeholder text for missing images, descriptions, and ratings.


## Design System Compliance
- **Component Verification**: All components used are part of the DESIGN_SYSTEM_DATA.
- **Variant Completeness**: All variants used are properly defined.
- **Text Property Mapping**: Text styles align with design system guidelines.
- **Schema Adherence**: All properties adhere to the design system's schema.
